# Installation:

1) Copy the source to your project dir

2) add the module to your local_settings.py:
   'CUSTOM_PAYMENT_MODULES' : [PROJECTNAME + '.payment.modules.paypal_express',],

3) Configure it in your http://www.store.com/settings

4) add this button/link to your base_cart.html:
  <a href="/checkout/paypal_express/"><img src="https://www.paypal.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_xpressCheckout.gif" alt="Pay With Paypal and Credit Cards" title="Pay With Paypal and Credit Cards"></a>

